    "key": "assign|The_tech_savant_is_more_technology_than_flesh_Cybernetics_coat|b3addc5a65c0",
    "original": "The tech savant is more technology than flesh. Cybernetics coat near every exposed inch of her body. Fingers augmented with digital interlinks wrap around the hilt of a sophisticated laser pistol. Other, nameless modifications poke through her paragon-branded jumpsuit, making her look a bit like a mechanical hedgehog. Empty, soulless eyes stare at you. Ehura owns her body now.",
